<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1009835>
    dc:description "FIGURE 55. Shells of Metalycaeus species. A – C. Metalycaeus rathouisianus (Heude, 1882). A. syntype (SMF 39243) of M. rathouisianus. B. syntype (MCZ 167209) of Alycaeus dolomiticus Heude, 1890. C. MCZ 167222, labelled as Alycaeus neglectus Heude, 1886. D. Metalycaeus sinensis (Heude, 1882) (lectotype, MCZ 167216). E. Metalycaeus (?) ibex Páll- Gergely & Hunyadi n. sp., (holotype, MNHN IM- 2012 - 27042). Scale represents 5 mm. All photos: B. Páll-Gergely." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1009835/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

